---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-academy-teal text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Getting Started</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-charcoal mb-4">
        From Inquiry to a Happier Dog — In 3 Simple Steps
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        No confusing process, no waitlist limbo. Here's exactly what happens next.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-academy-teal text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mx-auto mb-5 shadow-lg shadow-academy-teal/25">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-2">Submit Your Inquiry</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
          Fill out the form with your dog's details. Our team reviews every submission and reaches out — usually same day.
        </p>
        <!-- Connector arrow (hidden on mobile) -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-8 right-0 translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-0.5 bg-neutral-200"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-academy-teal text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mx-auto mb-5 shadow-lg shadow-academy-teal/25">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-2">In-Person Assessment</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
          Bring your dog in. Our trainers assess temperament, energy level, and social skills to determine the best fit — Daycare, Day & Train, or both.
        </p>
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-8 right-0 translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-0.5 bg-neutral-200"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-academy-teal text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mx-auto mb-5 shadow-lg shadow-academy-teal/25">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-2">Your Dog Starts Thriving</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
          Matched with compatible playmates, supervised by behaviour experts, and engaged in structured activities — your dog comes home calmer and happier.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-academy-teal text-white text-base font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-academy-teal-dark transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-academy-teal/25">
        Start With Step 1
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
